    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Gift Recommendations, Part 3\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to get gift recommendations for your friend.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Put your customized prompt from level 3 or a similar prompt in the chat. *Don't have a prompt? That's ok! You can copy one from below the instructions.*\r\n2. Pick a room image from the pre-loaded folder that matches your friend’s style.\r\n3. Add the image alongside your prompt.\r\n5. Add a sentence asking AI Chat to base its suggestions on the image.\r\n6. Press **Send** and read **AI Chat's response**.\r\n7. **Compare the response** to the one you received in Level 3. How did including an image change AI’s recommendations?\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>Give me 3 gift ideas under $30 for a 15-year-old girl who likes watercolor paintings. Her favorite birthday gift last year was a purple Polaroid camera.\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I add an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Add** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Attach**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n",
